  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cholera Response (I)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Following the spread of cholera to Port-au-Prince in early November, the IRC mobilized a strong prevention campaign in coordination with Haiti&#x2019;s public health sector, other humanitarian aid groups, and the Ministry of Health. Project activities included providing critical emergency response supplies, increasing access to life-saving treatment and information, improving public sanitation facilities, ensuring access to safe water and educating community members about ways to address the outbreak.</narrative>
  </description>
